rows.label: bf05160100_0010
rows.name:
Finally.
You took your sweet time.

rows.label: bf05160100_0020
rows.name: ...You're the...

rows.label: bf05160100_0030
rows.name: Hey, Turtle-chan!

rows.label: bf05160100_0040
rows.name: Hey.

rows.label: bf05160100_0050
rows.name:
You just don't give up, do you? C'mon,
out of the way.

rows.label: bf05160100_0060
rows.name: More like stubborn leech than turtle.

rows.label: bf05160100_0070
rows.name:
Hah. This time I'm here for something
a little bit different.

rows.label: bf05160100_0080
rows.name: Ugh, what's that supposed to mean?

rows.label: bf05160100_0090
rows.name: I want to see just how good you are, chum.

rows.label: bf05160100_0100
rows.name: I've been waiting here for three whole days already!

rows.label: bf05160100_0110
rows.name: Three days? Seriously?

rows.label: bf05160100_0112
rows.name: You know what, no thanks, I don't pick on idiots.

rows.label: bf05160100_0120
rows.name: Well then.

rows.label: bf05160100_0122
rows.name: Fight me and we'll see who's the idiot!

rows.label: bf05160100_0130
rows.name: How did you know that we'd be here...?

rows.label: bf05160100_0140
rows.name: I'll tell you...if you can beat me!

rows.label: bf05160100_0150
rows.name: You want to join the fun too?

rows.label: bf05160100_0160
rows.name: No, you all go ahead.

rows.label: bf05160100_0170
rows.name: Huh? Why?

rows.label: bf05160100_0180
rows.name:
What a shame! Looks like the illustrious
Flamebringer won't be helping you this time.

rows.label: bf05160100_0190
rows.name:
Thanks for the concern and all, but maybe you
should be worrying about yourself.

rows.label: bf05160100_0200
rows.name:
Big tree to your right, big rock to your left,
and a cliff right behind you.

rows.label: bf05160100_0210
rows.name: Which one's gonna get you this time, eh?

rows.label: bf05160100_0220
rows.name: Not today, furry ears.

rows.label: bf05160100_0222
rows.name: Check this.

rows.label: bf05160100_0230
rows.name: Whoa!

rows.label: bf05160100_0240
rows.name: What the-

rows.label: bf05160100_0250
rows.name:
Well?
Feel like taking me seriously yet, hmm?

rows.label: bf05160100_0260
rows.name: S-so strong...

rows.label: bf05160100_0270
rows.name:
What the...
How'd he do that?

rows.label: bf05160100_0280
rows.name: Thunderbolt Zeke.

rows.label: bf05160100_0290
rows.name:
Luxuria's most powerful Driver...and its
Crown Prince.

rows.label: bf05160100_0300
rows.name: Crown Prince of...Luxuria?!

rows.label: bf05160100_0310
rows.name: This guy?!

rows.label: bf05160100_0320
rows.name:
It is quite the rare opportunity to
see his...swordsmanship first-hand.

rows.label: bf05160100_0330
rows.name:
Now this is more like it. Ooh, come on,
yeah! Keep it coming!

rows.label: bf05160100_0340
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf05160100_0350
rows.name: That's it? That's all I get?!

rows.label: bf05160100_0360
rows.name: Ugh, fine.

rows.label: bf05160100_0370
rows.name:
...Anyway. Ready to concede
defeat to the Zekenator?

rows.label: bf05160100_0380
rows.name:
As if!
We're only just warming up, you pompous arse!

rows.label: bf05160100_0390
rows.name: I'm right with you. Let's show him what we got!

rows.label: bf05160100_0400
rows.name:
Hahaha, yessss! Let's see if the Aegis is worth
the hype!

rows.label: bf05160100_0402
rows.name: Hyaaah!
